text: Paolo Nocella is a former Australian politician. He was a Labor member of the South Australian Legislative Council from 10 October 1995, when he was appointed to a casual vacancy created by Mario Feleppa's resignation, to 1997, when he was defeated in the general election. ==References== Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:Members of the South Australian Legislative Council Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Australian Labor Party members of the Parliament of South Australia
